      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/649226599_18574618369041826_8519230123654932772_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1MDUyMTE2MTExNzA3NzgzNA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkyMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=Ru_kFRNZMCkQ7kNvwFYSwOq&amp;_nc_oc=AdorprF-dDBMxkXmNygMQbt7HmUhaGeW8_zMFU-RbB7KTfmkvaXJiRqKDAX-ZyKjHn0&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=FH0ISpsOCeDhbZsVuhgyFQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxJMkUNsjWf8wjLanLCP_7db4rfStJA8L3BQ45FPgLHDw&amp;oe=69CA14F7" alt="Instagram billede fra @sprngsmmr" /></p><p><strong>@sprngsmmr</strong></p><p>We’re excited to announce that Spring/Summer has been appointed as @argon18bike’s digital agency.<br/>
<br/>
Together with the Argon 18 team, we’re kicking off a new chapter in their digital journey - focused on building best-in-class digital experiences that bring the world famous cycling brand’s vision to life and support both internal teams and their global dealer network.<br/>
<br/>
Watch this space - we can’t wait to share more as it unfolds.</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/649226599_18574618369041826_8519230123654932772_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1MDUyMTE2MTExNzA3NzgzNA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkyMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=Ru_kFRNZMCkQ7kNvwFYSwOq&amp;_nc_oc=AdorprF-dDBMxkXmNygMQbt7HmUhaGeW8_zMFU-RbB7KTfmkvaXJiRqKDAX-ZyKjHn0&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=FH0ISpsOCeDhbZsVuhgyFQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxJMkUNsjWf8wjLanLCP_7db4rfStJA8L3BQ45FPgLHDw&amp;oe=69CA14F7" alt="Instagram billede fra @sprngsmmr" /></p><p><strong>@sprngsmmr</strong></p><p>We’re excited to announce that Spring/Summer has been appointed as @argon18bike’s digital agency.<br/>
<br/>
Together with the Argon 18 team, we’re kicking off a new chapter in their digital journey - focused on building best-in-class digital experiences that bring the world famous cycling brand’s vision to life and support both internal teams and their global dealer network.<br/>
<br/>
Watch this space - we can’t wait to share more as it unfolds.</p>]]></content:encoded>
